tes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not just report; we tell tales of stardom and stories untold.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it's the rise of a new sensation or the seasoned journey of an industry veteran, the TOI Entertainment Desk is your front-row seat to the fascinating narratives that shape the entertainment landscape.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times_of_India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.251983687080173e-19, \"text\": \"TOI\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times_of_India\"}, {\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Entertainment_Desk\", \"score\": 0.9999479053501619, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Entertainment Desk\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Entertainment_Desk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Entertainment_Desk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond the breaking news, we present a celebration of culture.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We explore the intersections of entertainment with society, politics, and everyday life.Read More  Chach benefits: 10 reasons to drink buttermilk with lunch everyday  8 Untold uses of onion beyond cooking  Pooja Hegde perfects the art of effortless 'girl-next-door' styling  Aishwarya to Ananya : Indian celebs who stole the limelight at Paris Fashion Week 2024  How to make protein-rich Paneer and Peanut Salad for fasting  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008b13 name suggestions for baby girls born during Navratri  8 effortless tips to impress your boss  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008b10 animals that bid farewell to God according to legend\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008b  10 reasons why the Japanese book \\u00e2\\u0